text: Jōetsu (上越) may refer to: *Jōetsu, Niigata, a city in Niigata Prefecture, Japan * Jōetsu Line, a major rail line in Japan * Jōetsu Shinkansen, a high- speed shinkansen railway line connecting Tokyo and Niigata * Jōetsumyōkō Station, a railway station in Jōetsu, Niigata * Jōetsu region, a geographical region in Niigata Prefecture or in the old provinces of Kōzuke and Echigo
title: Jōetsu
